# Local dev copy of the CV template — the root TEMPLATE_CV_EXPERT.docx is
# the source of truth and gets shipped to HF via the sync workflow. The
# backend copy here is only needed for the local uvicorn dev server.
backend/TEMPLATE_CV_EXPERT.docx
